Sample OmniOut Apps

Download, configure, and run OmniOut sample apps to view OmniOut app connection examples. Before You Begin: Add http://localhost:3000 to the Salesforce CORS allowlist.

SAMPLE APP

DESCRIPTION
EXAMPLE
PRODUCT

React, jsForce, and OAuth2
A react app that demonstrates login functionality using OAuth2 and jsForce.
Download and Run the OmniOut React-jsForce-OAuth2 Sample App

LWC
A single page app that's built using only Lightning web components.
Download and Run the OmniOut LWC Sample App

React, Express Proxy
A react app that demonstrates how to run an application using a proxy.
Download and Run the React-Express Proxy Sample App

Modify a Sample OmniOut for OmniScripts React App
Host LWC OmniScripts in your sample app by moving files from a compiled OmniOut project into your sample app.
